# G field

Add a column to a GORM model + its DTOs + a paired migration.

1. Ask the user for `<Resource> <field-name>:<type>`.
2. Run `gofasta g field <args> --dry-run --json` to preview.
3. Show the user the planned edits and the migration pair.
4. Re-run without `--dry-run` to apply if approved.
5. Always run `/migrate-explain` before applying the generated
   migration.
